= PagExamEn: Examination of Payments by FFII to contributors =
--> [:FfiiprojDonEn: Financing]
----

FFII cashflow should be supervised by a special supervising committee consisting mainly of donors and people who spend a lot of time for ffii without receiving money. 

For the time being, send funding requests to konto at ffii org, or, if "big money" is involved to eboard at ffii org.

See also
 * [:FfiiprojDonEn: FFII Project Financing and Donations]
